Text:
With `(>\s"\d*\.{0,1}\d*"\s\.$)` you can find both numbers if they are at the end of the line. Then you can just append `^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#float>` to that line.

Alternatively you can replace search for `(>\s"\d*\.{0,1}\d*"\s\.$)` and replace with `$1 ^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#float>` (tested with notepad++).
